# GRAPHICS::TOGGLE_PAUSED_RENDERPHASES

## Parameters
* **BOOL** on

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Toggles rendering of everything except PostFX. This freezes the screen before the UI pass.
